# Self-hosted Frontmatter YAML Profile

[yamlParse, yamlRenderResult](std/yaml-core.ssc)

```scalascript
val valid = List(
  "null",
  "enabled: true\nretries: 3\nratio: 1.25\nname: plain",
  "database:\n  url: \"jdbc:h2:mem:test\"\n  user: 'it''s-me'",
  "targets:\n  - jvm\n  - js\n  - wasm",
  "services:\n  - id: a\n    url: http://a\n  - id: b\n    url: http://b",
  "databases:\n  main:\n    url: jdbc:h2:mem:test\n    user: sa",
  "options: {jvm: true, retries: 3}\ntargets: [jvm, js, wasm]",
  "color: \"#fff\" # outside comment\nnote: hello # ignored",
  "literal: |\n  line one\n  line two\nfolded: >\n  hello\n  world"
)

for source <- valid do
  println(yamlRenderResult(yamlParse(source)))

val invalid = List(
  "a: 1\na: 2",
  "base: &base value",
  "copy: *base",
  "typed: !secret value",
  "<<: *base",
  "a: 1\n---\nb: 2",
  "%YAML 1.2\na: 1",
  "items: [a,]"
)

for source <- invalid do
  println(yamlRenderResult(yamlParse(source)))
```
